IMAPStore sanch-remote
Host imap.gmail.com
Port 993
UserCmd "pass google/sanch/username"
PassCmd "pass google/sanch/app_pass"
AuthMechs PLAIN
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore sanch-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.local/share/email/neomutt/mbsync/sanch/
Inbox ~/.local/share/email/neomutt/mbsync/sanch/INBOX
Flatten .

Channel sanch
Expunge Both
Far :sanch-remote:
Near :sanch-local:
Patterns * "INBOX" !"Inbox" !"[Gmail]/All Mail" !"[Gmail]/Important"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
################################################################### End profile

